<div class="content">
  <div class="info" id="firstText">
    <div class="icon">
      <%= image_tag 'software' %>
    </div>
    <div class="content contentRight">
      <span></span>
      <h1>Software</h1>
      <p>Packages are designed in such a manner that they cater all the possible software needs of any engineering firm. Our aim is to make engineering easy and we are committed to this by not only providing the ultimate solution but superior quality Technical support. Our Software list includes world’s finest software for all Engineering Disciplines.</p>
      <!-- <div class="moreRight moreDecor">Read More</div> -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info">
    <div class="content">
      <span></span>
      <h1>Training</h1>
      <p>Technical Trainings in this era is necessary to polish your skills. CompuSOFT Training Center caters this need in a very fine manner. Our trainer’s portfolio includes industry leading trainers with a massive field experience. Our state of art classes are one of its kind with full technology equipped equipment our classes offers a learning environment to the trainees.</p>
